  "detailed_description": "Island Paradise is a survival game where you build, upgrade and customize your own island and use nearby resources to create a home for future generations!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA strong storm forced the locals to leave the island.<br />\r\nNature has reborn an ecosystem untouched for hundreds of years...<br />\r\n<br />\r\n As you progress you will discover new technologies. You need to build bridges, so you can explore easily!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIsland Paradise is a vast and dynamic world with lakes, mountain ranges, caves, forests, jungles and abandoned houses where you can find shelter, food and places to buy and sell products!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTake care of nature and establish new settlements as part of your island building mission!",
  "about_the_game": "Island Paradise is a survival game where you build, upgrade and customize your own island and use nearby resources to create a home for future generations!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA strong storm forced the locals to leave the island.<br />\r\nNature has reborn an ecosystem untouched for hundreds of years...<br />\r\n<br />\r\n As you progress you will discover new technologies. You need to build bridges, so you can explore easily!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIsland Paradise is a vast and dynamic world with lakes, mountain ranges, caves, forests, jungles and abandoned houses where you can find shelter, food and places to buy and sell products!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTake care of nature and establish new settlements as part of your island building mission!",
